## objective
To apply HTML structure and CSSS styling techniques by creating a single webpage using inline, internal, and external CSS methods together with different CSS selectors

## what was done
. Create a web page containing:
  header section, navigation menu with anchor links, about section with paragraph with image, skills section using an unordered list, dairly routine section using an oredered list
. Applying CSS styling using:
  external, internal and inline CSS
. Demostrate different CSS selectors:
  element, class, Id, group, and Descedant selectors

## challenges faced
. linking the external CSS file correctly to the HTML document
. Understanding the difference between inline, internal,        and external CSS
. Making tyhe navigations links connects propery to the page    section using anchors

